    <item>
      <title>葛兰素史克药物在高级研究中有助于预防严重哮喘发作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gsk-drug-helps-prevent-severe-asthma-attacks-in-advanced-studies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葛兰素史克公司（GSK Plc）的实验药物在两项后期研究中有助于预防严重的哮喘发作，这为该药物的开发铺平了道路，该英国公司表示，该药物的年销售额可能达到 30 亿英镑（39 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/gsk-drug-helps-prevent-severe-asthma-attacks-in-advanced-studies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对 Apple iPhone 16 发布会的期待</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/can-apple-make-a-software-launch-sexy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果预计将发布新的 iPhone 16 系列手机，并对 Apple Watch 和 AirPods 耳机进行重大改进。这对可穿戴设备业务来说是一个重要时刻。Ed Ludlow 今早在库比蒂诺的 Apple Park 预告了“彭博监控”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/can-apple-make-a-software-launch-sexy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥年度通胀放缓，新一轮降息仍在继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/mexico-s-annual-inflation-slows-ahead-of-banxico-rate-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着食品价格飙升势头消退，墨西哥8月份年度通胀率基本与预期一致，这为央行本月考虑再次降息提供了更多空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/mexico-s-annual-inflation-slows-ahead-of-banxico-rate-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:14:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡债务大幅下降，因交易员认为政治风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/sri-lanka-debt-tumbles-as-investors-see-rising-political-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本月晚些时候大选前政治不确定性加剧，投资者减少了对斯里兰卡的投资，周一斯里兰卡美元债券的抛售加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/sri-lanka-debt-tumbles-as-investors-see-rising-political-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
